ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectIndian Residential Schools - FAA Sch.I.1 - ** Appropriate Minister **
PrecisAmendment to Schedule I.1 to the Financial Administration Act designating the MINISTER OF INDIAN AFFAIRS AND NORTHERN DEVELOPMENT as the appropriate Minister with respect to the OFFICE OF INDIAN RESIDENTIAL SCHOOLS RESOLUTION OF CANADA, effective May 19, 2006.
